annotationA: 28S ribosomal protein S15, mitochondrial; Essential for gut mitochondrial activity. Might be involved in tissue specific growth factor production; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uS15 family
annotationB: Ribosomal protein L36A, isoform A; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eL42 family
